            <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
              <text><citation jurisdiction="nz">Section <extref href="DLM436407">13(1)</extref> of the principal Act</citation> is amended by repealing <citation jurisdiction="nz">paragraph <extref href="DLM436407">(aa)</extref></citation>, and substituting
