                      <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="21.75*"/>
                      <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="74.25*"/>
                      <tbody>
                        <row>
                          <entry>1</entry>
                          <entry>The controlled drugs listed in the first column are presumed
to be for supply at and over the amount, level, or quantity listed
in the second column.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                          <entry>Morphine</entry>
                          <entry>5 grams, whether or not contained in a substance, preparation,
or mixture</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                          <entry>Cocaine</entry>
                          <entry>half a gram, whether or not contained in a substance, preparation,
or mixture</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
