                          <entry>half a gram, whether or not contained in a substance, preparation,
or mixture</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                          <entry>Lysergide</entry>
                          <entry>2 and a half milligrams or 25 flakes, tablets, capsules, or
other drug forms each containing some quantity of the drug</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                          <entry>DOB (2-amino-l-(4-bromo-2.5-dimethoxyphenyl) propane) (also
known as bromo-DMA)</entry>
                          <entry>100 milligrams or 25 flakes, tablets, capsules, or other drug
